## Installation
```sh
git clone https://github.com/your-repo/tea-smart-contract-framework.git
cd tea-smart-contract-framework
npm install
```

## Usage
### Deploy a Contract
```sh
npx tea-cli deploy path/to/contract
```

### Run Tests
```sh
npx tea-cli test
```

